{"tid":1287311,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡少芬首晒孕肚  張晉從後攬到實","createTime":"2019-07-05T06:59:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T09:17:33.000Z","uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"62933b6dd3b79adc484275ea5b9edddd60fc608c","tid":1287311,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:59:46.000Z","msg":"藝人蔡少芬（Ada）早前宣布為老公張晉佗第三胎，大家都為二人高興，仲叫Ada要小心佗B，咁啱佢哋依家正參與拍攝一個內地綜藝節目《我最愛的西女人們》，今日節目組就晒出二人最新合照，見Ada雖着寬鬆嘅衫，但仍難掩隆起嘅小腹，真係睇見都幸福！ <br />\n<br />\n合照中，兩人素顏出鏡一同溫馨睇日出，Ada靠喺老公懷中愜意眺望遠方，張晉則溫柔望實老婆，畫面溫馨。之後二人去到海邊，夫妻時而甜蜜對視，時而搭肩牽手並行，今次Ada個孕肚更加明顯，成個凸晒出嚟，其中一張相見張晉從後攬實Ada，二人又將手摸住Ada肚仔，呢個畫面確實係溫情四散，令人羨慕！"},{"pid":"d663ff7a3563d090a3620a125580ee26855c43b3","tid":1287311,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:00:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YW4DMPJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYW4DMPJ.png&h=0572cd67&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c629ee6d61238dc58ef0fd087c4a337e31c2fb2a","tid":1287311,"uid":12816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:00:46.000Z","msg":"馬英九睇錶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489ffc6fd054352c5bb4bc9e557d2fdf183130a4","tid":1287311,"uid":211914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:03:17.000Z","msg":"我最愛的西女人們<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b5cd5651e6981bb86405ce6ef3c86ddaf07fc4","tid":1287311,"uid":29702,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:08:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3128b231978179eb5ab867b83af85b384d29e31","tid":1287311,"uid":123115,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:09:39.000Z","msg":"其實點解成日分享埋啲大陸狗動向？"},{"pid":"7cc8ef13ea762e9d9738847d8fbc5a638bce003d","tid":1287311,"uid":8403